）的双重橙色乙烯基LP录制之外，发行版还包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/oasis">Oasis</a> ，他将在Vinyl上发行最佳收藏“ Time Flies”（1994-2009），这是Vinyl在Vinyl上首次提供的，这是Remastered Audio和全新的包装。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/taylor-swift">泰勒</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-cure">·</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">斯威夫特</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-hives">（</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lou-reed">Taylor</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gorillaz">Swift</a>以及<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/air">Air</a>的开创性“ Moon Safari”中的演示和现场直播的12英寸也只能在记录店当天购买。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/record-store-day-2025-full-list-releases-vinyl-3835631">在此处</a>找到RSD 2025版本的完整列表。</p><p>在其他新闻中，尽管“ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/music-sales-hit-20-year-high-but-beneath-the-surface-uk-artists-earn-far-below-average-salaries-3827139">地表之下，大多数英国艺术家的收入远低于平均水平</a>”， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/physical-music-sales-set-for-first-increase-in-20-years-3775262">但2024年的乙烯基和物理记录销售高20年。</a></p><p>约翰尼·马尔（Johnny Marr）与<a href="https://www.nme.com">曼彻斯特</a><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-honoured-as-record-store-legend-with-manchester-plaque-for-record-store-day-2025-3851584">（Manchester Plaque）的《唱片商店传奇》（Legend）表示敬意</a>。</p> ;
