x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/You-Me-At-Six-Biffy-2025-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/You-Me-At-Six-Biffy-2025-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/04/You-Me-At-Six-Biffy-2025-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/biffy-clyro">比菲·克莱罗（Biffy Clyro</a> ）的西蒙·尼尔（Simon Neil）在舞台上<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/you-me-at-six">六点加入了我的</a>行列，介绍了他们的歌曲“没人做得更好”  - 观看下面的录像。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/you-me-at-six-tell-josh-franceschi-interview-split-catfish-bottlemen-final-tour-3580717">您六点钟告诉我们他们的分裂：“这是一个严肃的弱者故事”</a></strong></li></ul><p>萨里五重奏即将在4月2日在O2学院布里克斯顿（O2 Academy Brixton）演出的第三局演出接近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/you-me-at-six-to-hold-wakes-ahead-of-final-uk-shows-buy-tickets-3800300">。</a></p><p>但是昨晚，摇滚歌手在袖子上感到非常惊讶。主持人乔什·弗朗西奇（Josh Franceschi）告诉人群：“今晚早些时候，我们在今晚早些时候谈论我们的关系 - 不仅与伦敦，而且是这个场所，”主唱乔什·弗朗西斯基（Josh Franceschi）告诉人群。 “我们降落在非常重要的事情上，这就是以下内容：&#39;没人做得更好&#39;。”</p><p>在发行歌曲之后（从您身上从您身上拿走了我的第三张专辑“<a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/you-me-at-six-sinners-never-sleep-first-listen-764238">Sinner Never Sleeply</a> ”），尼尔悄悄地在演出中途走到舞台上，与乐队一起演唱，这让球迷们的喜悦非常高兴。</p><p>在下面与西蒙·尼尔（Simon Neil）一起观看我的六场表演： </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="你在六英尺。西蒙·尼尔（Simon Neil） - 没有人会做得更好（Live，O2 Academy Brixton，伦敦2025年）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1AeVYTLOHOs?feature=oembed&enablejsapi=1" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/you-me-at-six-announce-split-and-2025-farewell-tour-now-is-a-good-time-to-call-time-3580114">您很快就会分开六点</a>，弗朗西斯（Franceschi）解释了乐队成立20周年是乐队始终旨在退休的里程碑。</p><p>他在一份声明中写道：“当我们开始YMA时，我们还是孩子。” “我们只希望长寿，旅行和体验一群朋友的生活。我们觉得自己是一支乐队20周年的前夕，现在是打电话时间的好时机。”</p><p>弗朗西斯（Franceschi） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/you-me-at-six-tell-josh-franceschi-interview-split-catfish-bottlemen-final-tour-3580717">在接受<em>NME</em>讲话时</a>阐述了：“这就像我们的童年迷恋，我们在一起已经20年了，并与之长大了。但是它比我们五岁要大得多。这完全脱离了我们对他人的意义。让我们有机会正确地说Goodbye，而不是滑出后门。”</p><p>乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/you-me-at-six-to-livestream-final-show-of-farewell-tour-announce-documentary-3845893">宣布，他们将在全球盛行的温布利秀上进行直播</a>，并分享说，纪录片被称为<em>“六部巡回演出”纪录片的最后</em>一晚（4月4日）。 </p><figure id="attachment_3843911" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3843911" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3843911" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing.jpg" alt="乔什·弗朗西斯（Josh Franceschi）在2023年雷丁音乐节（Reading Festival）的第1天进行六场演出。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/03/You-Me-At-Six-performing-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3843911" class="wp-caption-text"> Josh Franceschi of You Me at Six performs on day 1 of Reading Festival 2023. (Photo by Joseph Okpako/WireImage)</figcaption></figure><p> The tour film is set to get a world premiere on the same day and show a behind-the-scenes access-all-areas film shot across the whole tour. The dates kicked off in North America in October last year and since then have travelled through Europe and Australia, before finishing with a mammoth seven-week stint around the UK 